title: Ein Fall für Katharina Tempel
overview: Commissioner Katharina Tempel is moving from the LKA to the criminal investigation department in Hamburg. Under the leadership of her new superior, Chief Inspector Georg König, she begins the murder investigation in the Hanseatic city. She is supported by her new colleague Dela Tahiri, her husband Volker, the celebrated press spokesman for the Hamburg police, and her best friend and prosecutor Golda Hopkins.
